__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>32-bitowa liczba całkowita bez znaku określająca liczbę elementów w tablicy.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"header\" colspan=\"2\">Property attributes of <code>Array.prototype.length</code></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Writable</td>\n      <td>yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Enumerable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Configurable</td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">\n<h2 id=\"sk.c5.82adnia\" name=\"Sk.C5.82adnia\">Składnia</h2>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>arr</var>.length</code></pre>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wartością własności <code>length</code> jest dodatnia liczba całkowita mniejsza niż 2 do potęgi 32 (2<sup>32</sup>).</p>\n\n<p>W dowolnej chwili możesz ustalić wartość <code>length</code> w celu zmniejszenia rozmiaru tablicy. Ustawienie wartości <code>length</code> na większą niż rozmiar tablicy nie zwiększy liczby elementów, np. jeżeli ustawisz <code>length</code> na 3, podczas gdy obecną wartością jest liczba 2, tablica nadal będzie zawierać tylko 2 elementy.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_iteracja_przez_wszystkie_elementy_tablicy","title":"Przykład: Iteracja przez wszystkie elementy tablicy","isH3":true,"content":"<p>W poniższym przykładzie ilość elementów w tablicy <code>numbers</code> jest określana w instrukcji iteracyjnej na podstawie wartości <code>length</code>, następnie wartość każdego elementu jest podwajana.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> numbers <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  numbers<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// zawartość tablicy to teraz [2,4,6,8,10];</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_skracanie_tablicy","title":"Przykład: Skracanie tablicy","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniższy przykład zmniejsza rozmiar tablicy <code>statesUS</code> do 50, jeżeli przekracza on tę wartość.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>statesUS<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   statesUS<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">50</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect4\">&nbsp;</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"}],"summary":"32-bitowa liczba całkowita bez znaku określająca liczbę elementów w tablicy.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Array.prototype.length","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Array.prototype.length","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Array.prototype.length","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Array.prototype.length","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Array.length","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Array.length","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Array.prototype.length","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Array.length","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Array.length","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Array.length","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/length","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/length/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Dokumentacja referencyjna JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Obiekty"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array","title":"Array"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/length","title":"Array.prototype.length"}],"pageTitle":"Array.prototype.length - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}